Base R Boxplots

x <- rnorm(40, 5, 2)
y <- rnorm(40, 7, 5)
z <- rnorm(40, 3, 3)

normal

boxplot(x,y,z)

boxplot(x,y,z,
        horizontal = T)


notched boxplot

boxplot(x,y,z,
        notch = T, 
        col = c('firebrick', 'slateblue', 'turquoise'))


violin plot
